Windows usage of nameconverter.pl
Install strawberry Perl http://strawberryperl.com
edit nameconverter.pl (e.g. using http://notepad-plus-plus.org/download/v6.3.1.html)
change $naming to the file name of your cellbase conversion
change $dir    to the directory locating the lsm files

Click on windows symbol and type cmd in search programs and files
Go to the directory where nameconverter.pl is 
type: perl nameconverter.pl
